    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p>
                <hi rend="underline">Copy</hi>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">
                <placeName>Kingston Jamaica</placeName>
                <date>June 5/64</date>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <addressee>Mr. Light</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <placeName>New York</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir!</p>
            <p>It is with extreme regret that I am compelled<lb/> to announce to you the
                    <sic>impossibity</sic> of my<lb/> husband's addressing you by this present<lb/>
                Packet leaving today in consequence<lb/> of his having this morning commenced<lb/>
                to <add>Hebrew</add> having by English mail<lb/> of yesterday received the
                melancholy<lb/> intelligence of the death of his Revd<lb/> Father <add>Hebrew</add>.
                    <sic>The</sic> however desires his regrets<lb/> to you and begs you will in his name<lb/>
                <add>?</add> the unfortunate news to his respected<lb/> friend <persName>Revnd
                    Isaacs</persName> also with his best<lb/> regards</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I am Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">yours</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <persName role="author">K<add>?</add> Myers</persName>
            </p>
            <p>P.S.</p>
            <p>Pray request <persName>Rev Isaacs</persName> an obituary<lb/> inserted in messenger
                and <persName>Rev Leeser</persName><lb/> in Occident. His respected Father's<lb/>
                name was <persName>Moses. H. Myers</persName>, aged 62,<lb/>
                <del>my</del> over 30 years head master of Jewish<lb/> Free School,
                    <placeName>London</placeName> and one of the Ministers of<lb/> the great
                Synagogue of the same city.</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>
                <date>June 16th 1864</date>.</p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <add>Hebrew</add>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
